    {
      "instruction": "<p>Mix the <strong>roasted tomatoes</strong> and <strong>potatoes</strong> together on the tray and slice the <strong>cooked sausages</strong> in half lengthways on a clean chopping board</p><p>Top the<strong> warmed naan</strong> with the <strong>halved sausages</strong> and a <strong>fried egg</strong>, then dollop over the <strong>mint mayo</strong> and <strong>shallot salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>roasted tomatoes & potatoes</strong> to the side and drizzle the <strong>coriander chutney</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
